```{r survivalPlots, message = FALSE, warning = FALSE}
##load data
library(tidyverse)
out_list <- readRDS("survival_RNA.output_list.RDS")

#plot outputs from rpart survival
lapply(names(out_list), function(proj){
  
  ##get project data for rpart, median
  proj_out_list <- out_list[[proj]]
  rpart_out_list <- proj_out_list[["rpart_out_list"]]
  median_out_list <- proj_out_list[["median_out_list"]]
  
  ##apply over surv
  surv_vec <- c("DSS", "PFI")
  lapply(surv_vec, function(surv){
    for(x in seq_along(grep("not", rpart_out_list[[surv]]$rpart_surv_plots_list, invert = TRUE))){
      print(rpart_out_list[[surv]][["rpart_surv_plots_list"]][[x]])
    }
    for(x in seq_along(grep("not", median_out_list[[surv]]$median_surv_plots_list, invert = TRUE))){
      print(median_out_list[[surv]][["median_surv_plots_list"]][[x]])
    }
  })
})
```
